Items.text: You've been able to use your powers and be a force for good in the community.
Items.name: Ms Nice

Items.text: Now, you're going to choose your superhero name.
Items.name: Ms Nice

Items.text: The public is going to want to know who is helping them!
Items.name: Ms Nice

Items.text: Make sure to choose something you like.
Items.name: Ms Nice

Items.text: You won't be able to change it, at least this school year.
Items.name: Ms Nice
